name: The Frog Made of Jam
description:
Jam Frog is a frog made of jam. He is often left out of things, but he hopes to make a lot of friends  at the upcoming Frog Party. If he brings lots of flies, then he's sure to make lots of friends.

Play with WASD or Arrow Keys.
Up is jump. Down is duck.

Made in 2 days for the Frog Jam. (But I've updated the game since then.)
